WATCHING FROM THE SIDELINES.

294
00:13:28,384 --> 00:13:32,122
EXCEPT THEN, I HAD A HARD TIME
SEEING PEOPLE LIKE THAT.

295
00:13:32,222 --> 00:13:34,890
