00:13:34,991 --> 00:13:36,993
IN A VILLAGE LIKE THIS SOMEDAY?

297
00:13:38,228 --> 00:13:40,330
[TOYA]
UGH! MAN I AM BEAT!

298
00:13:40,430 --> 00:13:42,865
[RUDY] DUDE! EVERYONE
LOVED YOU OUT THERE!

