302
00:13:48,972 --> 00:13:50,240
[TOYA]
UH‐HUH...

303
00:13:50,340 --> 00:13:52,308
(DISTANT LAUGHTER AND CHATTER)
[TOYA] UH? HUH?

304
00:13:52,408 --> 00:13:54,577
[TOYA] WHOA...
THEY'RE STILL HYPED!

305
00:13:54,677 --> 00:13:57,080
[RUDY] TOO HYPER FOR ME...
BUT IT DOES MAKE ONE

306
