HOW CAN THEY TALK SO MUCH?

313
00:14:12,295 --> 00:14:14,164
IT'S BECAUSE
THEY'RE GIRLS, DUDE.

314
00:14:14,264 --> 00:14:18,801
VERY WELL. A GIRL THING... I
SUPPOSED I CAN UNDERSTAND THAT.

315
00:14:18,901 --> 00:14:22,038
AND I MUST ASSUME IT'S A GIRL
THING FOR ISUZU TO ACT

316
00:14:22,138 --> 00:14:23,706
