424
00:18:45,201 --> 00:18:47,403
ARE JUST HERE TO SAY
THEY'RE IN A GUILD, EINS!

425
00:18:47,503 --> 00:18:50,673
THEY DON'T LEAVE THE CITY LIMITS
TO HUNT OR GATHER, AND I DON'T

426
00:18:50,773 --> 00:18:54,710
THINK THEY'RE CRAFTING OR
SELLING ANYTHING EITHER!

427
00:18:54,810 --> 00:18:56,913
[HARUHARU]
HEH... NOTHING BUT PARASITES...

428
00:18:57,013 --> 00:19:00,050
TRUE, WE DIDN'T PICK UP A LOT OF
CONTRIBUTORS... HOWEVER...

429
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:02,252
[HARUHARU] "HOWEVER" WE DON'T
NEED A BUNCH OF LEACHES

430
00:19:02,352 --> 00:19:04,087
MAKING OUR GUILD SOFT AND LAZY!

431
00:19:04,187 --> 00:19:06,689
THE PEOPLE ARE STARTING
TO NOTICE, IN THE GUILD,

432
00:19:06,789 --> 00:19:09,059
IN THE CITY AND THEY'RE
NOT HAPPY ABOUT IT.

433
00:19:09,159 --> 00:19:11,794
IT IS ONLY A MATTER OF
TIME BEFORE IT BLOWS UP!

434
00:19:11,894 --> 00:19:13,029
I'M DOING EVERYTHING I CAN

435
00:19:13,129 --> 00:19:14,864
AT THE ROUND TABLE
CONFERENCE MEETINGS!

436
00:19:14,965 --> 00:19:16,766
[TOSHI] AND HOW ARE THEY
SUPPOSED TO FIX THIS?

437
00:19:16,866 --> 00:19:19,069
WE JUST NEED TO KICK THEM
OUT LIKE WE USED TO!

438
00:19:19,169 --> 00:19:20,870
[EINS] UH!
[HARUHARU] OR AT THE LEAST

439
00:19:20,971 --> 00:19:22,372
RESTRICT ENTRY INTO THE GUILD!

440
00:19:22,472 --> 00:19:23,873
I COULDN'T DO THAT!

441
00:19:23,974 --> 00:19:26,376
THE SOURCE OF OUR POLITICAL
CLOUT AT THE ROUND TABLE

442
00:19:26,476 --> 00:19:28,278
IS THE NUMBER OF
MEMBERS WE HAVE.

443
00:19:28,378 --> 00:19:31,247
RIGHT NOW, WE'RE THE THIRD
LARGEST GUILD IN AKIHABARA.

444
00:19:31,347 --> 00:19:32,882
WE CAN'T LOSE THAT.

445
00:19:32,983 --> 00:19:35,151
IF WE DON'T TRY TO
KEEP OUR NUMBERS UP

446
00:19:35,251 --> 00:19:38,621
THEN WE WON'T HAVE ANY SAY IN
WHAT GOES ON IN THOSE MEETINGS!

447
00:19:38,721 --> 00:19:40,590
[TOSHI]
WELL, I'LL TELL YOU THIS...

448
00:19:40,690 --> 00:19:42,392
I THINK OUR GUILD, AND
THE CITY AS A WHOLE

449
00:19:42,492 --> 00:19:46,963
WOULD BE BETTER OFF WITH FEWER
WELFARE CASES... "GUILD MASTER."

450
00:19:47,063 --> 00:19:48,231
[EINS]
MMM...

451
00:19:54,770 --> 00:19:55,471
[MINORI]
HUH?!

452
00:19:55,571 --> 00:19:57,373
(GASPING)

453
00:19:58,408 --> 00:19:59,976
[ISUZU]
ARE THOSE CHERRY BLOSSOMS?

454
00:20:00,076 --> 00:20:03,446
[SERARA] I THINK... I THINK
THEY'RE PLUM BLOSSOMS!

455
00:20:03,546 --> 00:20:07,117
[RUDY]
AH... THEY SMELL HEAVENLY!

456
00:20:11,487 --> 00:20:13,089
[TOYA]
YOU GOTTA BE KIDDING ME!

457
00:20:15,158 --> 00:20:19,062
AW, MAN! WE'RE NOT GETTING
ACROSS HERE ANYTIME SOON.

458
00:20:19,162 --> 00:20:21,297
[MINORI]
WE GOTTA FIND ANOTHER WAY.

459
00:20:24,935 --> 00:20:27,903
[MAN A] HELP! HELP US PLEASE!
(BOTH SURPRISED)

460
00:20:28,771 --> 00:20:31,607
(SCREAMING AND BREATHING HEAVY)

461
00:20:31,707 --> 00:20:32,475
[TOYA]
UH...!

462
00:20:32,575 --> 00:20:33,443
LOOK AT THAT!

463
00:20:33,543 --> 00:20:35,311
WE'VE GOT SOME OGRES!

464
00:20:35,411 --> 00:20:37,413
LET'S GET 'EM OFF THEIR BACKS!

465
00:20:37,513 --> 00:20:38,348
[ALL]
LET'S DO IT!

466
00:20:38,448 --> 00:20:39,950
(SCREAMING)
(GROWLS)

467
00:20:40,050 --> 00:20:43,153
[TOYA] NONE OF 'EM ARE OVER
LEVEL 22! THIS OUGHTA BE EASY!

468
00:20:43,253 --> 00:20:44,154
TOYA!

469
00:20:44,254 --> 00:20:45,121
[TOYA]
YEAH! I'M ON IT!

470
00:20:45,221 --> 00:20:47,690
TIME TO DIE YOU
UGLY PIECE‐A‐CRAP!

471
00:20:47,790 --> 00:20:49,659
(DEATH YELL)

472
00:20:50,226 --> 00:20:52,328
HMPH! SPEARS OF ICE!

473
00:20:54,164 --> 00:20:55,431
(FRIGHTENED)

474
00:20:55,531 --> 00:20:57,567
(GRUNTS)

475
00:20:57,567 --> 00:20:59,035
HMPH!

476
00:21:00,336 --> 00:21:02,505
[TOYA] ARE YOU GUYS
ALL RIGHT? YOU OKAY?

477
00:21:02,605 --> 00:21:05,208
[ROE2, DISTANT] YOU'VE GOT
COMPANY, LITTLE MAN! WATCH OUT!

478
00:21:05,308 --> 00:21:06,142
[TOYA]
HUH? WHA...?

479
00:21:06,242 --> 00:21:06,977
(STARTLED)

480
00:21:07,077 --> 00:21:08,411
[MINORI]
NIGHTSHADE SERVANTS!

481
00:21:08,511 --> 00:21:09,913
THEIR AVERAGE LEVEL IS...

482
00:21:10,013 --> 00:21:12,782
FORTY?! AND THERE'S
FIFTEEN OF THEM!

483
00:21:12,882 --> 00:21:14,217
SPIRIT MONSTERS:

484
00:21:14,317 --> 00:21:16,953
RESISTANT TO ATTACKS USING
POISON AND MENTAL POWERS,

485
00:21:17,053 --> 00:21:18,821
AND THEY'RE IMMUNE
TO INSTANT DEATH.

486
00:21:18,922 --> 00:21:21,224
FIGHTING THEM OFF
IS GONNA BE HARD!

487
00:21:21,324 --> 00:21:22,959
[MINORI, THINKING]
IF WE'RE NOT CAREFUL,

488
00:21:23,059 --> 00:21:24,694
SOME OF US COULD
GET SERIOUSLY HURT.

489
00:21:24,794 --> 00:21:26,262
[TOYA]
I'M GOING IN!

490
00:21:26,829 --> 00:21:28,364
(BATTLE GRUNT)

491
00:21:29,232 --> 00:21:31,134
[TOYA]
DID I EVEN DAMAGE THE THING?!

492
00:21:31,767 --> 00:21:33,103
WAUGH!

493
00:21:33,736 --> 00:21:34,604
[MINORI]
TOYA!

494
00:21:34,704 --> 00:21:36,739
(PAINFUL GRUNTS)

495
00:21:36,839 --> 00:21:38,274
(GROWLS)
[MINORI] HUH?

496
00:21:41,377 --> 00:21:42,345
(WINCE)

497
00:21:42,445 --> 00:21:44,214
[ROE2]
PRINCESS WRAITH!

498
00:21:45,181 --> 00:21:47,850
HWWAAH.

499
00:21:53,123 --> 00:21:54,490
EH.

500
00:21:55,358 --> 00:21:56,993
(GASP)

501
00:22:04,334 --> 00:22:05,835
WHAT THE...

502
00:22:13,143 --> 00:22:16,446
UM... EXCUSE ME...
BUT WHO ARE YOU?

503
00:22:16,546 --> 00:22:19,149
[ROE2]
MY NAME... IS ROE2

504
00:22:19,983 --> 00:22:21,884
I'M A SUMMONER BY TRADE

505
00:22:21,985 --> 00:22:24,287
AND SINCE I AM CURRENTLY
HEADED TO IKOMA,

506
00:22:24,387 --> 00:22:26,656
IT WOULDN'T BE TOO
MUCH OF A STRETCH...

507
00:22:26,756 --> 00:22:29,259
IF YOU CALLED ME A
TRAVELING VAMPIRE.

508
00:22:30,460 --> 00:22:32,262
ANOTHER VILLAIN IN GLASSES...

509
00:22:32,362 --> 00:22:33,429
[ALL]
MM‐HM!

510
00:22:33,529 --> 00:22:35,631
(ROE2 COLLAPSES)
[ALL] HUH?

511
00:22:35,731 --> 00:22:38,201
[ROE2] OH... THE SUN...
[ALL] HUH?!

512
00:22:38,301 --> 00:22:41,571
[ROE2] OH..THE SUN...! (MOANING)
[ALL] WHOA!

513
00:22:41,671 --> 00:22:44,774
[ROE2]
OHHH...! (MOANING)

514
00:24:15,431 --> 00:24:18,501
[AKATSUKI, VOICEOVER] THE NEW
MYSTERIOUS COMPANION IS ROE2.

515
00:24:18,601 --> 00:24:22,205
SHE FINDS JOY IN BEING
TREATED LIKE AN OLDER SISTER.

516
00:24:22,305 --> 00:24:24,274
TOYA AND THE OTHER JUNIOR
MEMBERS CONTINUE

517
00:24:24,374 --> 00:24:27,277
THEIR QUEST IN
SPITE OF HER ANTICS.

518
00:24:27,377 --> 00:24:29,445
ALONG THE WAY, THEY FIND
A GROUP OF ADVENTURERS WHO

519
00:24:29,545 --> 00:24:32,515
FIGHT MONSTERS TO PROTECT
THE PEOPLE OF THE LAND.

520
00:24:33,516 --> 00:24:36,186
[SHIROE] MY COMRADES
ARE ALWAYS BESIDE ME.

